> no longer works for today\u2019s AEC firms. To scale successfully, organizations need a structured AEC Project Management Ecosystem\u2122 that drives consistency, profitability, and strong PM talent development. In this webinar, Anthony Fasano, P.E., AEC PM, and author of Beyond PM Training, shares proven strategies for building scalable PM systems. You\u2019ll learn how to define PM roles and career paths, assess development gaps, standardize tools, and onboard PMs more effectively. Walk away with a practical blueprint to move beyond generic training and build a sustainable project management framework that drives results.<\/p>","pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"section"},{"id":"78e062ab","settings":{"editor":"<p class=\"fl-heading\"><b>Your Presenter<\/b><\/p>","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":30,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"700","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"30","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","__globals__":{"text_color":"globals\/colors?id=primary"}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"70e56efd","settings":{"editor":"<h2 class=\"fl-heading\"><b>Anthony Fasano, P.E., AEC PM | Engineering Management Institute<\/b><\/h2>","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"774737be","settings":{"editor":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Anthony-Fasano.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-55130 size-medium\" title=\"Anthony Fasano, P.E., AEC PM\" src=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Anthony-Fasano-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"EMI- Your Engineering Career\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" \/><\/a><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Most AEC organizations are too busy to focus on attracting, developing, and retaining talented professionals, making it hard to grow. Through his work a tEMI, Fasano utilizes a proven framework to help organizations, both public and private, build professional development plans, programs, and tools that help them attract, build, AND maintain strong teams and grow sustainably.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fasano has written a bestselling book entitled <\/span><b><i>Engineer Your Own Success <\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(by IEEE-Wiley Press)<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, and under his stewardship, EMI has built a massive content platform including 10 active podcasts, 3 YouTube channels, and a popular blog dedicated to helping AEC professionals become better managers and leaders.<\/span><\/p>","_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"50","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"}],"settings":{"template":"elementor_canvas"},"metadata":{"_yoast_wpseo_content_score":"60","be_title_toggle_hide":"1","_yoast_wpseo_estimated-reading-time-minutes":"2","disable_sitewide_popup":"a:1:{i:0;s:4:\"true\";}","_yoast_wpseo_wordproof_timestamp":